      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-alf-mag-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      14                   to   v-car                  .
           move      17                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      22                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rig-alf-mag        to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-alf-mag-999.
           exit.

