           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      33                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rig-tip-ubi-des    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-rig-ubi-des-999.
