      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-prm-ubi (1)    to   w-all-str-alf          .
           move      07                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           perform   all-str-ble-000      thru all-str-ble-999        .
           if        w-all-str-flg        not  = spaces
                     go to acc-rig-ub1-100.
