      *                  * Eventuale compattamento ubicazioni          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-prm-ubi (2)    to   w-rig-prm-ubi (1)      .
           move      w-rig-prm-ubi (3)    to   w-rig-prm-ubi (2)      .
